  • INTERFACE
    • An interface for Activities on different types
    ActivityConnection
    after  Returns the elements in the list that come after the specified cursor.
    String
    before  Returns the elements in the list that come before the specified cursor.
    String
    first  Returns the first _n_ elements from the list.
    Int
    last  Returns the last _n_ elements from the list.
    Int
    {direction: ASC, field: created_at}
    order_by  ActivityOrderInput
    updated_at_after  A timestamp encoded as a string that. When provided, only activities with a updated_at greater than this value will be resolved. Example: activities(updated_at_after: "2017-11-30 13:37:12 UTC")
    String
    types  [ActivityTypes]
    not_types  [ActivityTypes]
    internal  [Boolean]
